response.original_title: Wow! Wow! Wubbzy!: The Best Of Wubbzy
response.overview: We asked Wubbzy fans worldwide - especially parents - to choose their favorite episodes via Facebook, and these are the Wow Wow Winners! In these all-time best adventures, Wubbzy helps baby chirpees who've lost their mother, Widget builds a robot to teach a lesson about cheating, Daizy gets a visit from a fill-in Tooth Fairy, Wubbzy wants to be the star of Walden's play, the town of Wuzzleburg misunderstands a friendly dinosaur game, and everybody has fun on the first day of spring. There's plenty of singing, dancing, important social skills, and a kickedy-kick ball gone plooey too, all in the first collection chosen by you!
response.title: Wow! Wow! Wubbzy!: The Best Of Wubbzy
